<span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="font-style: italic">Ability</span></span> is what you're capable of doing. <span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="font-style: italic">Motivation</span></span> determines what you do. <span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="font-style: italic">Attitude</span></span> determines how well you do it. - Lou Holtz</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
